<!doctype html>

<html>

<head>
  <title>TBone's Bike Shop</title>
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<meta chatset="UTF-8">
<style>
#spacing-div {
  height: 75px;
}

body {
  background-color: black;
  color: white;
  font-family: verdana, sans-serif;
}

header {
  position: fixed;
  display: flex;
  height: 75px;
  width: 100%;
  background-color: white;
}

.brand {
  display: inline-block;
  width: 40%;
  min-width: 430px;
  height: 75px;
}

#header-img {
  margin: 15px;
  display: inline-block;
}

#nav-brand {
  box-sizing: border-box;
  color: black;
  display: inline-block;
  margin-bottom: 50px;
  vertical-align: top;
}

#nav-bar {
  display: flex;
  background-color: white;
  width: 60%;
  justify-content: space-evenly;
}

ul {
  width: 100%;
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-evenly;
  padding: 0;
}

li {
  list-style-type: none;
 
}

.nav-link {
  text-decoration: none;
  color: orange;
  font-size: 25px;
}

.nav-link:hover {
  color: orangered;
}

#bikes, #parts, #service {
  display: flex;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  justify-content: space-evenly;
}

.product-card {
  min-width: 300px;
  max-width: 450px;
  height: fit-content;
  min-height: 5px;
  background-color: orange;
  border: 5px solid orange;
  border-radius: 10px;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  margin-bottom: 5px;
}

.subtitle {
  display: block;
  text-align: center;
  width: 100%;
}

.product-img {
  width: 100%;
}

.text-center {
  text-align: center;
}

.bold {
  font-weight: bold;
}

#video {
  min-width: 300px;
  width: 420px;
  height: 250px;
}

input, textarea {
  display: block;
  margin: 5px;
}
select, label {
  text-align: initial;
  margin: 5px;
}

footer {
  width: 100%;
  min-height: 100px;
  height: fit-content;
  background-color: gray;
  text-align: center;
  padding-bottom: 5px;
}

hr {
  padding: 5px;
  width: 75%;
  border-bottom: 1px solid black;
  border-top: none;
  border-left: none;
  border-right: none;

 
}

#service .product-card {
  height: 385px;
  width: 420px;
  padding: 15px;
}


@media (max-width: 750px) {

  #spacing-div {
  height: 150px;
  }
 
  header {
    display: block;
    background-color: white;
  }
  nav {
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }
  .brand {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    margin: 0;
    border: none;
  }
 
  #nav-bar {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    margin: 0;
    border: none;
  }
}

@media (max-width: 450px) {
 
  #nav-brand {
    font-size: 20px;
    margin-top: 25px;
  }
 
  #video {
    width: auto;
  }
 
  #nav-bar {
    display: block;
  }
 
  div {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
  }
 
  textarea {
    cols: 30;
  }
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<header id="header">
  <div class="brand">
    <img id="header-img" src="https://tbonesbikeworld.com/logo.jpg">
    <h1 id="nav-brand">TBone's Bike Shop</h1>
  </div>
  <nav id="nav-bar">
    <ul>
      <li><a class="nav-link" href="#bikes">Bikes</a></li>
      <li><a class="nav-link" href="#parts">Parts</a></li>
      <li><a class="nav-link" href="#service">Service</a></li>
    </ul>
  </nav>
</header>

<div id="spacing-div"></div>

<div id="bikes">

  <h2 class="subtitle">Bikes</h2>

  <div class="product-card">

    <h3 class="text-center">Rad Runner</h3>
    <img class="product-img" src="https://www.wearethecyclists.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/RadRunner-1-Utility-Ebike-accesories-2048x1420.jpg">
    <div class="info">
      <p class="bold">$1,699</p>
      <p>500w motor</p>
      <p>672wh battery</p>
    </div>

  </div>


  <div class="product-card">

    <h3 class="text-center">Super 73 RX Malibu</h3>
    <img class="product-img" src="https://images.ctfassets.net/tu8gkjqcgjw9/2mt7aglUCy14UNp3bUsIZF/f7099adcce274051422b5633ac997132/Super73_RSD-Malibu_White_02_RtSide_Web.jpg?w=750&h=500&fl=progressive&q=85&fm=jpg">
    <div class="info">
      <p class="bold">$5,699</p>
      <p>2000w motor</p>
      <p>960wh battery</p>
    </div>

  </div>

  <div class="product-card">

    <h3 class="text-center">Arial Rider - Grizzly 52v</h3>
    <img class="product-img" src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0065/6549/4839/products/grizzlye-bikesag_1728x.jpg?v=1605176189">
    <div class="info">
      <p class="bold">$5,399</p>
      <p>Dual 1000w motor</p>
      <p>1,820wh Dual battery</p>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>

<div id="parts">

  <h2 class="subtitle">Parts</h2>

  <div class="product-card">



    <h3 class="text-center">52v Shark Battery</h3>
    <img class="product-img" src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0537/7176/3911/products/48V-Shark-Long-Range-17.5Ah-Ebike-Battery_BafangUSAdirect_EbikeEssentials_3310da99-acdf-45b4-82ec-59712a16259a_1024x1024.jpg?v=1625164137">
    <div class="info">
      <p class="bold">$850</p>
      <p>52v</p>
      <p>910wh</p>
    </div>

  </div>

  <div class="product-card">

    <h3 class="text-center">Color Display LCD</h3>
    <img class="product-img" src="https://www.hi-scooter.net/Uploads/pro/5c0a1251c3b82.png">
    <div class="info">
      <p class="bold">$99</p>
      <p>Works with all ebikes</p>
      <p>Bright color information</p>
    </div>

  </div>

  <div class="product-card">

    <h3 class="text-center">1000w Race Motor</h3>
    <img class="product-img" src="https://cyclingindustry.news/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/bafang-lead.jpg">
    <div class="info">
      <p class="bold">$500</p>
      <p>Works with all ebikes</p>
      <p>Top speed 70km/h</p>
    </div>

  </div>

</div>

<div id="service">
  <h2 class="subtitle">Service</h2>

  <div class="product-card">
    <h3 class="text-center">Full Tune Up</h3>
    <p class="bold">$75</p>
    <p>To keep your bike in the best shape, and running smoothly for years, make sure to keep it tuned up!</p>
    <p>Full tune up includes: brake tuneup, oil chain, wash, and a free sticker!</p>
  </div>

  <div class="product-card">
    <h3 class="text-center">Maintenance Tips</h3>
    <iframe id="video" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/kE5E8FVNelI" title="YouTube video player" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen></iframe>
    <p>Check out this YouTube video for some maintenance tips you can do at home!</p>
  </div>

  <div class="product-card">
    <h3 class="text-center">Repairs/Upgrades</h3>
    <p>Let us know what you need and well send back a quote within 5 mins!</p>
    <form id="form" action="https://www.freecodecamp.com/email-submit">
      <input type="text" name="name" placeholder="name">
      <input id="email" type="email" placeholder="your@email.com" name="email">
      <label for="make">Bike Brand</label>
      <select id="make">
        <option value="Brand">Brand</option>
        <option value="Brand">Rad Power</option>
        <option value="Brand">Super 73</option>
        <option value="Brand">Ariel Rider</option>
        <option value="Brand">Juiced</option>
        <option value="Brand">Emmo</option>
      </select>

      <textarea cols="40" rows="6" placeholder="What do you need? eg. bike repair, motor upgrade, new battery, etc"></textarea>
      <input id="submit" type="submit">
    </form>
  </div>

</div>

<footer>
  <hr>
  <p>TBone's Bike Shop</p>
  <p>Toronto, Ontario</p>
  <p>The Worlds Best Bikes!</p>
  <hr>
</footer>
</body>
</html>
